Описание:
Sybase is providing a free edition of Adaptive Server version 12.5.3 ESD#1 on Linux for Intel x86 (32-bit).
This version, called Adaptive Server Enterprise Linux Express Edition, does not require a license.This Linux Express Edition has the following configuration limitations:
• You can specify only one engine in the max online engines configuration parameter.
• You can configure up to 2GB of max memory.
• The total disk space is limited to 5GB.За раздачу спасибо пользователю generalx2000
